title: On Site Maintenance, We Make House Calls! - US Rubber Lofts (A-110)
description: Do you want the privacy of a home but the convenience of an apartment? Then Butcher Block Mill is perfect for you! Private entry, two stories, plenty of closet space! These newly constructed townhomes offer a new perspective on community living.

These units have modern soft close cabinets, glimmering granite counter tops, and a full size washer and dryer! Cozy up by your very own fireplace and gaze onto the Providence River through your over-sized windows. The original hardwood floors can be found on the top floor of this beautifully remodeled building. Designer paint colors give the townhomes a fresh modern look while retaining the historic feel.

We have incredible amenities too! Work out at our on-site gym or catch some sun on the roof top deck! Having a party? Reserve the community room! Watch the big game in our theater room, or catch it in the game room while shooting pool!

Be close to all of the action at Butcher Block Mill. Atwell’s avenue is blocks away, where great food and friendly faces await you. You’re only a 20 minute walk from downtown where you can catch memorable events like water fire, or go get something cool at the Sunday flea market!

title: The Lifestyle You Deserve - US Rubber Lofts (A-103)
description: Do you want the privacy of a home but the convenience of an apartment? Then Butcher Block Mill is perfect for you! Private entry, two stories, plenty of closet space! These newly constructed townhomes offer a new perspective on community living.

These units have modern soft close cabinets, glimmering granite counter tops, and a full size washer and dryer! Cozy up by your very own fireplace and gaze onto the Providence River through your over-sized windows. The original hardwood floors can be found on the top floor of this beautifully remodeled building. Designer paint colors give the townhomes a fresh modern look while retaining the historic feel.

We have incredible amenities too! Work out at our on-site gym or catch some sun on the roof top deck! Having a party? Reserve the community room! Watch the big game in our theater room, or catch it in the game room while shooting pool!

Be close to all of the action at Butcher Block Mill. Atwell’s avenue is blocks away, where great food and friendly faces await you. You’re only a 20 minute walk from downtown where you can catch memorable events like water fire, or go get something cool at the Sunday flea market!

title: PC STUDENT RENTAL FULLY Furnished
description: A 3 BEDROOM RENTAL, FULLY FURNISHED WITH HEAT AND ELECTRIC AND ALL UTILITIES !
This spacious apartment is located on the first floor of a historic home built in the 1940s. While the space has been recently renovated, some old-world charm, like the detailed woodwork, remains.

Step inside and make yourself at home in the kitchen, fully equipped with all of your essential appliances. If you're not in the mood to cook, a plethora of dining options can be found within minutes of your home base! Check out Los Andres for a Peruvian-style dish or indulge in Italian cuisine at Camille's.

Should you choose to dine in, you'll have plenty of seating options between the breakfast bar and dining room. With large windows, hardwood floors, and contemporary furnishings, the dining area is the perfect spot for at-home meals.
Continue the evening's entertainment in downtown Providence, or relax here in the living room. The flat-screen cable TV and book collection are sure to keep you entertained!
Each bedroom, including the converted den, features a full-sized bed. Sleep soundly on the soft linens and wake to natural light pouring in through the abundant windows!
THE LOCATION
About 2 blocks away lies Providence College. The campus is comprised of 105 acres and is the only college or university in the US founded by and conducted under the auspices of the Dominican Friars.
Ten minutes away is Johnson & Wales University, home of the Wildcats. Rhode Island School of Design RISD is also just a quick 1.6-mile drive away.

Spend time at Water place Park, just 7 minutes away. This great park is a hub for art installations and concerts, and connects to other downtown walking paths. Be sure to plan your trip around the Water Fire Providence, a truly urban experience!

In downtown Rhode Island, you can expect to find fun and historic monuments like the 1871 Soldiers' and Sailors' Monument, the Superman Building, the Providence Performing Arts Center, and the Dunkin' Donuts Center! These attractions and more are only 10 minutes from home.
ADDITIONAL DETAILS
Key Residence Features:
-fully furnish, TV, high ceilings, double windows, hardwood floors, new furnishings, shared coin-op laundry machines in the basement and parking for 3/4 vehicles in the driveway
- Convenient Providence location 2 blocks from Providence College, 10 minutes from Johnson & Wales University, Brown University and downtown, and 7 minutes from Water place Park
- Nearest Commercial Airport: T. F. Green Airport - 2000 Post Rd, Warwick, RI 02886, (~10 miles away)

- Nearby Medical Centers: VA Medical Center ~ 0.7 Miles, Roger Williams Medical Center ~ 0.7 miles, Hasboro Children's Hospital - 3 miles, Rhode Island Hospital ~ 3.1 miles, Women and Infants Hospital ~ 3 miles
- Nearby Universities: Rhode Island School of Design RISD ~ 1.6 miles, Johnson and Wales ~ 1.7 miles, Providence College ~ 0.8 miles

title: BEWARE IF CONTACTED ABOUT A RENTAL
description: Hi!
Just wanted to let fellow renters to know about a landlord in the Elmhurst area.
I am moving out and when I say living there has been a nightmare, it would be an understatement. Because I am moving out, she may be looking to rent again and this method is how she found me.
The street address is MODENA AVE, Providence.

If anyone wants to email, I can give you the details and also include pictures I have been taking for a year. My biggest concern is I do not want someone to go thru what I have, the landlord seems to think that she is allowed in your apartment with no notice and she goes thru your personal things. I had to install a camera and I have video/pictures/etc.
There is way more details to some of the other things she does (thinks it funny to over water her plants knowing if she does it rains down on me while in bed)
I would just like to help someone who is looking for a cheap place to rent. The cheap rent is not worth the day to day harassment.
